Class EnemyNode

java.lang.Object
com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity.node.movable.MovableNode
com.platformer.escape_beyond.model.entity.node.movable.enemy.EnemyNode
Direct Known Subclasses:
FireDragonNode, MummyNode
public class EnemyNode extends MovableNode
Represents an enemy node in the game. An enemy node extends the MovableNode class and includes a type to specify the enemy's characteristics (e.g., "fire_dragon", "mummy"). It also contains a Node object for graphical or logical representation.
